	<description>ARTIO JoomSEF rewrites Joomla! URLs to be Search Engine Friendly together advanced
	URL editing options, such as metatags definitions. It integrates FaLang and native Joomla! multilanguage support with
	option of internationalized, multilingual URLs. The configuration is easy and straightforward.
	Support for many further popular extensions is included!</description>

